{"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp","name":"Junction","system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p id=\"docs-internal-guid-8dc90b9d-7fff-b2e7-f72b-7a6eabae7afa\" dir=\"ltr\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-2ef3209f-7fff-d528-48a5-c85a7619c9cf\">If your next action is to Cast a non-emanation Spell, designate its targeted location, even if it targets one creature. Instead of firing immediately, this spell will activate at the start of your next turn, targeting the designated square(s), regardless of your new position. If there is no valid target, the spell fails. Any damage or healing effects of this spell are doubled. Enemies can tell that you have cast a spell, and that it will take effect soon, but are not aware of its targeting.</span></p>\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-1d0bc7ae-7fff-bc1b-1dab-549ad6b2b115\"> </span></p>"},"source":{"value":"Pathfinder Advanced Player's Guide"},"rules":[],"slug":"junction","schema":{"version":0.833,"lastMigration":null},"traits":{"value":["metamagic","hb_red-mage"],"rarity":"common"},"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"offensive"},"actions":{"value":1},"requirements":{"value":""},"trigger":{"value":""},"deathNote":false,"weapon":{"value":""}},"type":"action","flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.dCuvfq3r2K9wXY9g"}},"effects":[],"ownership":{"default":0,"OUUN90EiIqJoMi8x":3,"Wc7yEAoFhLUF8cPX":3},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.9.3","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679990638566,"modifiedTime":1680766527811,"lastModifiedBy":"Wc7yEAoFhLUF8cPX"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"6SCRM0Lumbq2IBB6"}
